{"tid":5710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Plan B]梁頌恆 在的士中抗爭","createTime":"2016-11-27T04:38:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-16T00:24:07.000Z","uid":7832,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f8cb323f756f5e8f7a94a125f255ca576289c1e1","tid":5710,"uid":7832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T04:38:36.000Z","msg":"#立場 : //青年新政梁頌恆今日亦有現身論壇，被記者問及對彭定康的演說有何意見，他形容對方是一貫英國保守黨的説法。他指大家都知道自由、民主、法治很重要，但對香港人而言，要問的是如何才能維持維持這些價值。<br />\n<br />\n對於彭定康昨日批評港獨是破壞了香港人的道德高地，梁今日指出2014年（佔領運動）結果已告訴大家，道德高地並不能守住這些價值。<br />\n<br />\n他又指希望能在論壇上向彭定康發問，「想問作為香港最後一位港督，作為英國政壇有影響力的人，他面對香港今日的狀況，是否在他預期之內，又是否如他所說，建立道德高地就能解決？」//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%A2%81%E9%A0%8C%E6%81%86-%E5%BD%AD%E5%AE%9A%E5%BA%B7%E6%BC%94%E8%AA%AA%E6%98%AF%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%88%E9%BB%A8%E4%B8%80%E8%B2%AB%E8%AA%AC%E6%B3%95-%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E9%AB%98%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%AE%88%E4%BD%8F%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%83%B9%E5%80%BC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25A2%2581%25E9%25A0%258C%25E6%2581%2586-%25E5%25BD%25AD%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%25BA%25B7%25E6%25BC%2594%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E6%2598%25AF%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AE%2588%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25B2%25AB%25E8%25AA%25AC%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E7%25AB%258B%25E9%2581%2593%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%25AE%2588%25E4%25BD%258F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2583%25B9%25E5%2580%25BC%2F&d=%2BtbibQSoubMVXvrlaH3wycW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=09bea06d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25A2%2581%25E9%25A0%258C%25E6%2581%2586-%25E5%25BD%25AD%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%25BA%25B7%25E6%25BC%2594%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E6%2598%25AF%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AE%2588%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25B2%25AB%25E8%25AA%25AC%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E7%25AB%258B%25E9%2581%2593%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E9%25AB%